extends layout.pug

block content
  h2 New Booking Alert

  p A new booking has been created:

  table(style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;")
    tr
      th(style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") Client
      td(style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") #{user.firstName} #{user.lastName}

    tr
      th(style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") Service
      td(style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") #{booking.serviceName}

    tr
      th(style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") Date & Time
      td(style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") #{booking.dateFormatted} at #{booking.timeFormatted}

    tr
      th(style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") Contact
      td(style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;")
        | Phone: #{user.phone}
        br
        | Email: #{user.email}

    if booking.specialRequests
      tr
        th(style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") Special Requests
        td(style="padding: 8px; border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;") #{booking.specialRequests}

  p.
    Please review this booking in the admin panel to confirm or reschedule if needed.

  a.button(href=`${siteUrl}/admin/appointments`) View in Admin Panel